  <TKKN_Sculpture_Shell.label>海贝壳</TKKN_Sculpture_Shell.label>
  <TKKN_Sculpture_Shell.description>这个美丽而坚固的壳来自已经死掉的海洋生物。</TKKN_Sculpture_Shell.description>
  <TKKN_Sculpture_Shell_Blueprint_Install.label>海贝壳（蓝图）</TKKN_Sculpture_Shell_Blueprint_Install.label>

  <TKKN_RedwoodDead.label>红木</TKKN_RedwoodDead.label>
  <TKKN_RedwoodDead.description>一棵巨大的，非常缓慢生长的树。它的根很浅，当它长得太大时，它颠覆了。\n\n产生红木，这是珍贵的稀有木材。</TKKN_RedwoodDead.description>

  <TKKN_Lava_Spring.label>喷发的岩浆</TKKN_Lava_Spring.label>
  <TKKN_Lava_Spring.description>喷涌的岩浆，硬化后成为熔岩石。</TKKN_Lava_Spring.description>

  <TKKN_ColdSpring.label>冷泉</TKKN_ColdSpring.label>
  <TKKN_ColdSpring.description>冰澈的地下水，这些水会让四周保持凉爽。</TKKN_ColdSpring.description>

  <TKKN_OasisSpring.label>绿洲</TKKN_OasisSpring.label>
  <TKKN_OasisSpring.description>冰澈的地下水，这些水会让四周保持凉爽。</TKKN_OasisSpring.description>

  <TKKN_HotSpring.label>温泉</TKKN_HotSpring.label>
  <TKKN_HotSpring.description>温暖的地热泉水，这些泉水具有治疗功效。</TKKN_HotSpring.description>

  <TKKN_SteamVent.label>蒸汽喷泉</TKKN_SteamVent.label>
  <TKKN_SteamVent.description>由熔岩而产生的天然蒸汽。</TKKN_SteamVent.description>

  <TKKN_SteamGenerator.label>蒸汽发电机</TKKN_SteamGenerator.label>
  <TKKN_SteamGenerator.description>用蒸汽喷泉发电，必须放置在蒸汽喷泉上。</TKKN_SteamGenerator.description>
  <TKKN_SteamGenerator_Blueprint.label>蒸汽发电机（蓝图）</TKKN_SteamGenerator_Blueprint.label>
  <TKKN_SteamGenerator_Blueprint_Install.label>蒸汽发电机（蓝图）</TKKN_SteamGenerator_Blueprint_Install.label>
  <TKKN_SteamGenerator_Frame.label>蒸汽发电机（建造中）</TKKN_SteamGenerator_Frame.label>
  <TKKN_SteamGenerator_Frame.description>用蒸汽喷泉发电，必须放置在蒸汽喷泉上。</TKKN_SteamGenerator_Frame.description>


